So I quit my job.

00:21:18.944 --> 00:21:20.860
And I had a month of
unemployment where I just

00:21:20.860 --> 00:21:23.950
locked myself in my apartment,
and I learned the trombone

00:21:23.950 --> 00:21:24.890
from scratch.

00:21:24.890 --> 00:21:28.270
So I used the foundation that
I had with brass instruments

00:21:28.270 --> 00:21:30.610
and just transferred
it to low brass.

00:21:30.610 --> 00:21:33.820
But yeah, I've also went to
school for musical theater,

00:21:33.820 --> 00:21:36.110
so I've been singing for
a very long time as well.

00:21:36.110 --> 00:21:38.680
So it's kind of an amalgamation
of all of the weird things

00:21:38.680 --> 00:21:39.680
that I like to do.

00:21:39.680 --> 00:21:40.750
So it's a dream job.

00:21:40.750 --> 00:21:42.100
It's great.

00:21:42.100 --> 00:21:42.600
Andrew.

