make your own choices

00:48:39.250 --> 00:48:43.584
versus taking what the, I
guess, original actor has done?

00:48:43.584 --> 00:48:44.750
LAURA OSNES: Great question.

00:48:44.750 --> 00:48:45.920
ALAN SEALES: Great
question, yeah.

00:48:45.920 --> 00:48:46.640
ANDREW LEGGIERI: Good que--

00:48:46.640 --> 00:48:47.848
I'll figure that out tonight.

00:48:47.848 --> 00:48:51.275
[LAUGHTER]

00:48:54.410 --> 00:48:56.930
Yeah, it would be my
first time doing this part

00:48:56.930 --> 00:48:58.761
with these guys.

00:48:58.761 --> 00:49:00.510
And I've been with the
show for two years,

00:49:00.510 --> 00:49:03.260
so this is going to be a
whole whirlwind of emotions

00:49:03.260 --> 00:49:07.580
and a whole whirlwind of,
am I in the right spot?

00:49:07.580 --> 00:49:09.290
Am I saying the right line?

00:49:09.290 --> 00:49:10.570
What's my next prop?

00:49:10.570 --> 00:49:13.010
What's my next costume change?

00:49:13.010 --> 00:49:16.850
So yeah, it's going
to be a lot of--

00:49:16.850 --> 00:49:19.280
I think tonight is going
to be a lot of, just,

00:49:19.280 --> 00:49:21.080
what I've worked on and what--

00:49:21.080 --> 00:49:22.371
LAURA OSNES: Hitting the notes.

00:49:22.371 --> 00:49:26.720
ANDREW LEGGIERI: --and going
to be as close to the show

00:49:26.720 --> 00:49:29.340
as they know it,
because otherwise,

00:49:29.340 --> 00:49:32.150
for me, I don't know, my mind
will be in a million places.

00:49:32.150 --> 00:49:37.070
So yeah, I think the
first time I went on

00:49:37.070 --> 00:49:42.480
for one of the other tracks, it
was very much saying the words,

00:49:42.480 --> 00:49:43.940
making sure I have a character.

00:49:43.940 --> 00:49:45.890
And then as I kept doing it--

00:49:45.890 --> 00:49:47.746
I did it four times so far--

00:49:47.746 --> 00:49:49.370
I felt like I was
able to flesh it out.

00:49:49.370 --> 00:49:51.060
I was living in it more.

00:49:51.060 --> 00:49:55.040
And it's not that I was
making different choices

00:49:55.040 --> 00:49:59.810
from the other actor, but
we're just different people.

00:49:59.810 --> 00:50:02.780
So it felt like when I
was living in it more,

00:50:02.780 --> 00:50:06.260
I was bringing something to
it that only I can bring,

00:50:06.260 --> 00:50:07.580
where I'm only me.

00:50:07.580 --> 00:50:10.670
I can't really
replicate anything.

00:50:10.670 --> 00:50:14.765
But the more comfortable
I feel, then I

00:50:14.765 --> 00:50:15.890
feel like I can live in it.

00:50:15.890 --> 00:50:18.630
And it's probably going
to be different, for sure.

00:50:18.630 --> 00:50:22.220
But yeah, I hope that
answered your question.

